=====<u>Connectivity Test</u>=====
Originally introduced in ''RESONARK 4 -ELVES- Part 2: Raylight,'' this is a mode consisting of a selected series of songs the player must go through with set conditions. 

Functioning similar to beatmaniaIIDX's CLASS mode, the player is given either a BASIC or STRICT route for completion, one providing a much more difficult goal than the other. For example, a course requiring no more than 10 misses applies to '''the entire course''', not per song. Completing either route will unlock the subsequent locked Class. 

There are currently six Classes to select, three of which are unlocked at the start.

