===== <u>Story</u> =====
The year Resonark 4.1 and 4.2 takes place in is untold, however it is implied that it takes place at least a few years after a piano performance competition between two rival girls, Cian and Honoka. In separate instances, both girls stumble upon an abandoned mine with mysterious cables and scaffolding wired up to a strange, massive vault. With how this mine was constructed, it boasted an unheard of set of enhanced acoustics, causing the girls to play different songs to experiment with their musical performances. 

One day, while Honoka played with the Instrument that reverberated across the entire shaft, Cian was hiding away within the scaffolding, hearing the beautiful sounds coming from Honoka's Instrument, amazed by her technique and performances. As the time went on, the two began to grasp a hold of their emotions, reuniting with a common passion for music and grand curiosity, their reunion possibly being the key to opening the mysterious vault...

